# Advanced Minesweeper (Single HTML File)

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Advanced Minesweeper</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.5);
        }

        .game-container {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .controls {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .difficulty {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        button.active {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .stat {
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            min-width: 80px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .board {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(var(--cols), 30px);
            grid-template-rows: repeat(var(--rows), 30px);
            gap: 2px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .cell {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background-color: #333;
            border-radius: 3px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.1s;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .cell:hover {
            background-color: #444;
        }

        .cell.revealed {
            background-color: #252525;
            cursor: default;
        }

        .cell.flagged {
            background-color: #4a2e2e;
        }

        .cell.mine {
            background-color: #f44336;
        }

        .cell.mine-revealed {
            background-color: #ff0000;
        }

        .number-1 { color: #2196F3; }
        .number-2 { color: #4CAF50; }
        .number-3 { color: #f44336; }
        .number-4 { color: #3F51B5; }
        .number-5 { color: #795548; }
        .number-6 { color: #607D8B; }
        .number-7 { color: #212121; }
        .number-8 { color: #9C27B0; }

        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .modal-content {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        .modal h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .modal button {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .hint-btn {
            background-color: #FF9800;
        }

        .hint-btn:hover {
            background-color: #FF5722;
        }

        .theme-toggle {
            background-color: #9C27B0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .cell {
                width: 25px;
                height: 25px;
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .controls {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .stats {
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: space-between;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Advanced Minesweeper</h1>

    <div class="game-container">
        <div class="controls">
            <div class="difficulty">
                <button id="easy-btn" class="active">Easy</button>
                <button id="medium-btn">Medium</button>
                <button id="hard-btn">Hard</button>
                <button id="custom-btn">Custom</button>
            </div>

            <button id="theme-toggle" class="theme-toggle">ðŸŒ™ Dark Mode</button>
        </div>

        <div class="controls">
            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat">Mines: <span id="mines-count">10</span></div>
                <div class="stat">Flags: <span id="flags-count">0</span></div>
                <div class="stat">Time: <span id="time">0</span></div>
            </div>

            <button id="new-game-btn">New Game</button>
            <button id="hint-btn" class="hint-btn">Hint</button>
        </div>

        <div id="board" class="board"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="game-over-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h2 id="game-result">You Won!</h2>
            <p id="game-stats">Time: 0 seconds</p>
            <button id="play-again-btn">Play Again</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="custom-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h2>Custom Game</h2>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <label for="custom-rows">Rows (5-30):</label>
                <input type="number" id="custom-rows" min="5" max="30" value="10" style="width: 60px; margin-left: 10px;">
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <label for="custom-cols">Columns (5-30):</label>
                <input type="number" id="custom-cols" min="5" max="30" value="10" style="width: 60px; margin-left: 10px;">
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <label for="custom-mines">Mines (10-50%):</label>
                <input type="number" id="custom-mines" min="3" max="300" value="10" style="width: 60px; margin-left: 10px;">
            </div>
            <button id="start-custom-btn">Start Game</button>
            <button id="cancel-custom-btn" style="margin-left: 10px;">Cancel</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Game state
        let board = [];
        let rows = 10;
        let cols = 10;
        let minesCount = 10;
        let flagsCount = 0;
        let revealedCount = 0;
        let gameOver = false;
        let firstClick = true;
        let timer = 0;
        let timerInterval = null;
        let hintUsed = false;
        let darkMode = true;

        // DOM elements
        const boardElement = document.getElementById('board');
        const minesCountElement = document.getElementById('mines-count');
        const flagsCountElement = document.getElementById('flags-count');
        const timeElement = document.getElementById('time');
        const gameOverModal = document.getElementById('game-over-modal');
        const gameResultElement = document.getElementById('game-result');
        const gameStatsElement = document.getElementById('game-stats');
        const playAgainBtn = document.getElementById('play-again-btn');
        const newGameBtn = document.getElementById('new-game-btn');
        const hintBtn = document.getElementById('hint-btn');
        const themeToggleBtn = document.getElementById('theme-toggle');
        const customModal = document.getElementById('custom-modal');

        // Difficulty buttons
        const easyBtn = document.getElementById('easy-btn');
        const mediumBtn = document.getElementById('medium-btn');
        const hardBtn = document.getElementById('hard-btn');
        const customBtn = document.getElementById('custom-btn');
        const startCustomBtn = document.getElementById('start-custom-btn');
        const cancelCustomBtn = document.getElementById('cancel-custom-btn');

        // Initialize game
        function initGame() {
            // Clear existing board
            boardElement.innerHTML = '';
            board = [];
            flagsCount = 0;
            revealedCount = 0;
            gameOver = false;
            firstClick = true;
            hintUsed = false;

            // Stop timer if running
            if (timerInterval) {
                clearInterval(timerInterval);
                timerInterval = null;
            }
            timer = 0;
            updateTimeDisplay();

            // Update mines count display
            minesCountElement.textContent = minesCount;
            flagsCountElement.textContent = flagsCount;

            // Set CSS variables for grid size
            boardElement.style.setProperty('--rows', rows);
            boardElement.style.setProperty('--cols', cols);

            // Create board
            for (let r = 0; r < rows; r++) {
                board[r] = [];
                for (let c = 0; c < cols; c++) {
                    board[r][c] = {
                        isMine: false,
                        isRevealed: false,
                        isFlagged: false,
                        adjacentMines: 0
                    };

                    const cell = document.createElement('div');
                    cell.className = 'cell';
                    cell.dataset.row = r;
                    cell.dataset.col = c;

                    // Event listeners
                    cell.addEventListener('click', () => handleLeftClick(r, c));
                    cell.addEventListener('contextmenu', (e) => {
                        e.preventDefault();
                        handleRightClick(r, c);
                    });

                    boardElement.appendChild(cell);
                }
            }
        }

        // Place mines after first click (to ensure first click is always safe)
        function placeMines(firstRow, firstCol) {
            let minesPlaced = 0;

            while (minesPlaced < minesCount) {
                const r = Math.floor(Math.random() * rows);
                const c = Math.floor(Math.random() * cols);

                // Don't place mine on first click or where a mine already exists
                if ((r !== firstRow || c !== firstCol) && !board[r][c].isMine) {
                    board[r][c].isMine = true;
                    minesPlaced++;
                }
            }

            // Calculate adjacent mines for each cell
            for (let r = 0; r < rows; r++) {
                for (let c = 0; c < cols; c++) {
                    if (!board[r][c].isMine) {
                        board[r][c].adjacentMines = countAdjacentMines(r, c);
                    }
                }
            }

            // Start timer after mines are placed
            startTimer();
        }

        // Count adjacent mines for a cell
        function countAdjacentMines(r, c) {
            let count = 0;

            // Check all 8 surrounding cells
            for (let dr = -1; dr <= 1; dr++) {
                for (let dc = -1; dc <= 1; dc++) {
                    if (dr === 0 && dc === 0) continue; // Skip current cell

                    const nr = r + dr;
                    const nc = c + dc;

                    // Check if neighbor is within bounds and is a mine
                    if (nr >= 0 && nr < rows && nc >= 0 && nc < cols && board[nr][nc].isMine) {
                        count++;
                    }
                }
            }

            return count;
        }

        // Handle left click
        function handleLeftClick(r, c) {
            if (gameOver || board[r][c].isFlagged) return;

            // On first click, place mines (avoiding this cell)
            if (firstClick) {
                placeMines(r, c);
                firstClick = false;
            }

            // If clicked on a mine
            if (board[r][c].isMine) {
                revealMines();
                gameOver = true;
                endGame(false);
                return;
            }

            // Reveal cell if not already revealed
            if (!board[r][c].isRevealed) {
                revealCell(r, c);

                // Check for win condition
                checkWin();
            } else {
                // If clicking on a revealed number, try chord action
                chordCells(r, c);
            }
        }

        // Handle right click (flag)
        function handleRightClick(r, c) {
            if (gameOver || board[r][c].isRevealed) return;

            const cell = getCellElement(r, c);

            if (!board[r][c].isFlagged) {
                board[r][c].isFlagged = true;
                cell.textContent = 'ðŸš©';
                flagsCount++;
            } else {
                board[r][c].isFlagged = false;
                cell.textContent = '';
                flagsCount--;
            }

            flagsCountElement.textContent = flagsCount;
        }

        // Reveal a cell
        function revealCell(r, c) {
            if (board[r][c].isRevealed || board[r][c].isFlagged) return;

            const cell = getCellElement(r, c);
            board[r][c].isRevealed = true;
            cell.classList.add('revealed');
            revealedCount++;

            if (board[r][c].adjacentMines > 0) {
                cell.textContent = board[r][c].adjacentMines;
                cell.classList.add(`number-${board[r][c].adjacentMines}`);
            } else {
                // If no adjacent mines, reveal all adjacent cells recursively
                for (let dr = -1; dr <= 1; dr++) {
                    for (let dc = -1; dc <= 1; dc++) {
                        if (dr === 0 && dc === 0) continue; // Skip current cell

                        const nr = r + dr;
                        const nc = c + dc;

                        // Check if neighbor is within bounds
                        if (nr >= 0 && nr < rows && nc >= 0 && nc < cols) {
                            revealCell(nr, nc);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        // Chord action (when clicking on a revealed number)
        function chordCells(r, c) {
            const cell = board[r][c];
            if (!cell.isRevealed || cell.adjacentMines === 0) return;

            // Count adjacent flags
            let adjacentFlags = 0;
            for (let dr = -1; dr <= 1; dr++) {
                for (let dc = -1; dc <= 1; dc++) {
                    if (dr === 0 && dc === 0) continue;

                    const nr = r + dr;
                    const nc = c + dc;

                    if (nr >= 0 && nr < rows && nc >= 0 && nc < cols && board[nr][nc].isFlagged) {
                        adjacentFlags++;
                    }
                }
            }

            // If flags match adjacent mines, reveal all unflagged adjacent cells
            if (adjacentFlags === cell.adjacentMines) {
                for (let dr = -1; dr <= 1; dr++) {
                    for (let dc = -1; dc <= 1; dc++) {
                        if (dr === 0 && dc === 0) continue;

                        const nr = r + dr;
                        const nc = c + dc;

                        if (nr >= 0 && nr < rows && nc >= 0 && nc < cols && 
                            !board[nr][nc].isRevealed && !board[nr][nc].isFlagged) {

                            if (board[nr][nc].isMine) {
                                revealMines();
                                gameOver = true;
                                endGame(false);
                                return;
                            }

                            revealCell(nr, nc);
                        }
                    }
                }

                // Check for win condition after chording
                checkWin();
            }
        }

        // Reveal all mines (when game is lost)
        function revealMines() {
            for (let r = 0; r < rows; r++) {
                for (let c = 0; c < cols; c++) {
                    if (board[r][c].isMine) {
                        const cell = getCellElement(r, c);
                        cell.textContent = 'ðŸ’£';
                        cell.classList.add(board[r][c].isFlagged ? 'flagged' : 'mine-revealed');
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        // Check if player has won
        function checkWin() {
            if (revealedCount === (rows * cols - minesCount)) {
                gameOver = true;
                endGame(true);
            }
        }

        // End game (win or lose)
        function endGame(isWin) {
            // Stop timer
            if (timerInterval) {
                clearInterval(timerInterval);
                timerInterval = null;
            }

            // Flag all mines if won
            if (isWin) {
                for (let r = 0; r < rows; r++) {
                    for (let c = 0; c < cols; c++) {
                        if (board[r][c].isMine && !board[r][c].isFlagged) {
                            board[r][c].isFlagged = true;
                            const cell = getCellElement(r, c);
                            cell.textContent = 'ðŸš©';
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            // Show game over modal
            gameResultElement.textContent = isWin ? 'You Won! ðŸŽ‰' : 'Game Over! ðŸ’¥';
            gameStatsElement.textContent = `Time: ${timer} seconds | Mines: ${minesCount} | Size: ${rows}x${cols}`;
            gameOverModal.style.display = 'flex';
        }

        // Start timer
        function startTimer() {
            timer = 0;
            updateTimeDisplay();
            timerInterval = setInterval(() => {
                timer++;
                updateTimeDisplay();
            }, 1000);
        }

        // Update time display
        function updateTimeDisplay() {
            timeElement.textContent = timer;
        }

        // Get cell DOM element
        function getCellElement(r, c) {
            return document.querySelector(`.cell[data-row="${r}"][data-col="${c}"]`);
        }

        // Set difficulty
        function setDifficulty(difficulty) {
            switch (difficulty) {
                case 'easy':
                    rows = 10;
                    cols = 10;
                    minesCount = 10;
                    break;
                case 'medium':
                    rows = 16;
                    cols = 16;
                    minesCount = 40;
                    break;
                case 'hard':
                    rows = 16;
                    cols = 30;
                    minesCount = 99;
                    break;
                case 'custom':
                    // Custom settings handled separately
                    return;
            }

            // Update active button
            easyBtn.classList.remove('active');
            mediumBtn.classList.remove('active');
            hardBtn.classList.remove('active');
            customBtn.classList.remove('active');

            document.getElementById(`${difficulty}-btn`).classList.add('active');

            initGame();
        }

        // Show hint (reveal a safe cell)
        function showHint() {
            if (gameOver || firstClick || hintUsed) return;

            // Find all unrevealed, unflagged, non-mine cells
            const safeCells = [];
            for (let r = 0; r < rows; r++) {
                for (let c = 0; c < cols; c++) {
                    if (!board[r][c].isRevealed && !board[r][c].isFlagged && !board[r][c].isMine) {
                        safeCells.push({ r, c });
                    }
                }
            }

            if (safeCells.length > 0) {
                // Pick a random safe cell
                const { r, c } = safeCells[Math.floor(Math.random() * safeCells.length)];

                // Temporarily highlight the cell
                const cell = getCellElement(r, c);
                cell.style.backgroundColor = '#FF9800';
                cell.style.boxShadow = '0 0 10px #FF9800';

                setTimeout(() => {
                    cell.style.backgroundColor = '';
                    cell.style.boxShadow = '';
                }, 1000);

                hintUsed = true;
                hintBtn.disabled = true;
            }
        }

        // Toggle theme
        function toggleTheme() {
            darkMode = !darkMode;

            if (darkMode) {
                document.body.style.backgroundColor = '#121212';
                document.body.style.color = '#e0e0e0';
                document.querySelector('.game-container').style.backgroundColor = '#1e1e1e';
                themeToggleBtn.textContent = 'ðŸŒ™ Dark Mode';
            } else {
                document.body.style.backgroundColor = '#f5f5f5';
                document.body.style.color = '#333';
                document.querySelector('.game-container').style.backgroundColor = '#fff';
                themeToggleBtn.textContent = 'â˜€ï¸ Light Mode';
            }
        }

        // Event listeners
        easyBtn.addEventListener('click', () => setDifficulty('easy'));
        mediumBtn.addEventListener('click', () => setDifficulty('medium'));
        hardBtn.addEventListener('click', () => setDifficulty('hard'));
        customBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            customModal.style.display = 'flex';
            document.getElementById('custom-rows').value = rows;
            document.getElementById('custom-cols').value = cols;
            document.getElementById('custom-mines').value = minesCount;
        });

        newGameBtn.addEventListener('click', initGame);
        playAgainBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            gameOverModal.style.display = 'none';
            initGame();
        });

        hintBtn.addEventListener('click', showHint);
        themeToggleBtn.addEventListener('click', toggleTheme);

        startCustomBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const customRows = parseInt(document.getElementById('custom-rows').value);
            const customCols = parseInt(document.getElementById('custom-cols').value);
            const customMines = parseInt(document.getElementById('custom-mines').value);

            // Validate inputs
            if (customRows < 5 || customRows > 30 || 
                customCols < 5 || customCols > 30 || 
                customMines < 3 || customMines > Math.floor(customRows * customCols * 0.5)) {
                alert('Invalid settings! Please check your inputs.');
                return;
            }

            rows = customRows;
            cols = customCols;
            minesCount = customMines;

            customModal.style.display = 'none';

            // Update active button
            easyBtn.classList.remove('active');
            mediumBtn.classList.remove('active');
            hardBtn.classList.remove('active');
            customBtn.classList.add('active');

            initGame();
        });

        cancelCustomBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            customModal.style.display = 'none';
        });

        // Initialize game on load
        initGame();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

This advanced Minesweeper game includes:

1. **Multiple Difficulty Levels**: Easy (10x10 with 10 mines), Medium (16x16 with 40 mines), Hard (16x30 with 99 mines)
2. **Custom Game Mode**: Set your own board size and mine count
3. **Game Features**:
   - Left click to reveal cells
   - Right click to place/remove flags
   - Chord action (clicking on revealed numbers with correct flag count)
   - Hint system (highlights a safe cell)
   - Timer and mine counter
4. **Visual Enhancements**:
   - Color-coded numbers
   - Dark/light mode toggle
   - Animated hints
   - Responsive design for mobile
5. **Game States**:
   - Win/lose detection
   - Game over modal with stats
   - First click always safe

The entire game is contained in a single HTML file with embedded CSS and JavaScript.

# Advanced Minesweeper with Animations (Single HTML File)

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Advanced Minesweeper</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #121212;
            --text-color: #e0e0e0;
            --container-bg: #1e1e1e;
            --button-bg: #333;
            --button-hover: #4CAF50;
            --mine-color: #f44336;
            --flag-color: #4a2e2e;
            --revealed-color: #252525;
            --highlight-color: #FF9800;
            --shadow-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .light-mode {
            --bg-color: #f5f5f5;
            --text-color: #333;
            --container-bg: #fff;
            --button-bg: #e0e0e0;
            --button-hover: #4CAF50;
            --mine-color: #f44336;
            --flag-color: #ffcdd2;
            --revealed-color: #f5f5f5;
            --highlight-color: #FF9800;
            --shadow-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.5s ease, color 0.5s ease;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.5);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        .game-container {
            background-color: var(--container-bg);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--shadow-color);
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            transition: background-color 0.5s ease, box-shadow 0.5s ease;
            animation: slideUp 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        .controls {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .difficulty {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        button {
            background-color: var(--button-bg);
            color: var(--text-color);
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        button::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 5px;
            height: 5px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            opacity: 0;
            border-radius: 100%;
            transform: scale(1, 1) translate(-50%);
            transform-origin: 50% 50%;
        }

        button:focus:not(:active)::after {
            animation: ripple 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: var(--button-hover);
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        button.active {
            background-color: var(--button-hover);
            font-weight: bold;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .stat {
            background-color: var(--button-bg);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            min-width: 80px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in;
        }

        .stat span {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        .board {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(var(--cols), 30px);
            grid-template-rows: repeat(var(--rows), 30px);
            gap: 2px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            perspective: 1000px;
        }

        .cell {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background-color: var(--button-bg);
            border-radius: 3px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            user-select: none;
            position: relative;
            transform-style: preserve-3d;
        }

        .cell::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .cell:hover {
            background-color: var(--button-hover);
        }

        .cell:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .cell.revealed {
            background-color: var(--revealed-color);
            cursor: default;
            animation: flipIn 0.3s ease-out;
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
        }

        .cell.flagged {
            background-color: var(--flag-color);
            animation: pulse 0.5s ease;
        }

        .cell.mine {
            background-color: var(--mine-color);
        }

        .cell.mine-revealed {
            background-color: var(--mine-color);
            animation: shake 0.5s ease;
        }

        .number-1 { color: #2196F3; }
        .number-2 { color: #4CAF50; }
        .number-3 { color: #f44336; }
        .number-4 { color: #3F51B5; }
        .number-5 { color: #795548; }
        .number-6 { color: #607D8B; }
        .number-7 { color: #212121; }
        .number-8 { color: #9C27B0; }

        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 100;
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-out;
        }

        .modal-content {
            background-color: var(--container-bg);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
            transform: scale(0.9);
            opacity: 0;
            animation: modalAppear 0.3s forwards 0.1s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: background-color 0.5s ease;
        }

        .modal h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-top: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
        }

        .modal button {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .hint-btn {
            background-color: #FF9800;
        }

        .hint-btn:hover {
            background-color: #FF5722;
        }

        .theme-toggle {
            background-color: #9C27B0;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { 
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to { 
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes flipIn {
            0% {
                transform: rotateY(0deg);
                background-color: var(--button-bg);
            }
            100% {
                transform: rotateY(180deg);
                background-color: var(--revealed-color);
            }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            10%, 30%, 50%, 70%, 90% { transform: translateX(-2px); }
            20%, 40%, 60%, 80% { transform: translateX(2px); }
        }

        @keyframes ripple {
            0% {
                transform: scale(0, 0);
                opacity: 0.5;
            }
            100% {
                transform: scale(20, 20);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @keyframes modalAppear {
            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes highlight {
            0% { 
                background-color: var(--highlight-color);
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--highlight-color);
            }
            100% { 
                background-color: var(--revealed-color);
                box-shadow: none;
            }
        }

        @keyframes explode {
            0% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: scale(5);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        /* Particle effect for win */
        .confetti {
            position: absolute;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background-color: #f00;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: confettiFall 3s ease-out forwards;
        }

        @keyframes confettiFall {
            0% { 
                transform: translateY(-100px) rotate(0deg);
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% { 
                transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(360deg);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .cell {
                width: 25px;
                height: 25px;
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .controls {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .stats {
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: space-between;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Advanced Minesweeper</h1>

    <div class="game-container">
        <div class="controls">
            <div class="difficulty">
                <button id="easy-btn" class="active">Easy</button>
                <button id="medium-btn">Medium</button>
                <button id="hard-btn">Hard</button>
                <button id="custom-btn">Custom</button>
            </div>

            <button id="theme-toggle" class="theme-toggle">ðŸŒ™ Dark Mode</button>
        </div>

        <div class="controls">
            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat">Mines: <span id="mines-count">10</span></div>
                <div class="stat">Flags: <span id="flags-count">0</span></div>
                <div class="stat">Time: <span id="time">0</span></div>
            </div>

            <button id="new-game-btn">New Game</button>
            <button id="hint-btn" class="hint-btn">Hint</button>
        </div>

        <div id="board" class="board"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="game-over-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h2 id="game-result">You Won!</h2>
            <p id="game-stats">Time: 0 seconds</p>
            <button id="play-again-btn">Play Again</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="custom-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h2>Custom Game</h2>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <label for="custom-rows">Rows (5-30):</label>
                <input type="number" id="custom-rows" min="5" max="30" value="10" style="width: 60px; margin-left: 10px;">
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <label for="custom-cols">Columns (5-30):</label>
                <input type="number" id="custom-cols" min="5" max="30" value="10" style="width: 60px; margin-left: 10px;">
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <label for="custom-mines">Mines (10-50%):</label>
                <input type="number" id="custom-mines" min="3" max="300" value="10" style="width: 60px; margin-left: 10px;">
            </div>
            <button id="start-custom-btn">Start Game</button>
            <button id="cancel-custom-btn" style="margin-left: 10px;">Cancel</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Game state
        let board = [];
        let rows = 10;
        let cols = 10;
        let minesCount = 10;
        let flagsCount = 0;
        let revealedCount = 0;
        let gameOver = false;
        let firstClick = true;
        let timer = 0;
        let timerInterval = null;
        let hintUsed = false;
        let darkMode = true;

        // DOM elements
        const boardElement = document.getElementById('board');
        const minesCountElement = document.getElementById('mines-count');
        const flagsCountElement = document.getElementById('flags-count');
        const timeElement = document.getElementById('time');
        const gameOverModal = document.getElementById('game-over-modal');
        const gameResultElement = document.getElementById('game-result');
        const gameStatsElement = document.getElementById('game-stats');
        const playAgainBtn = document.getElementById('play-again-btn');
        const newGameBtn = document.getElementById('new-game-btn');
        const hintBtn = document.getElementById('hint-btn');
        const themeToggleBtn = document.getElementById('theme-toggle');
        const customModal = document.getElementById('custom-modal');

        // Difficulty buttons
        const easyBtn = document.getElementById('easy-btn');
        const mediumBtn = document.getElementById('medium-btn');
        const hardBtn = document.getElementById('hard-btn');
        const customBtn = document.getElementById('custom-btn');
        const startCustomBtn = document.getElementById('start-custom-btn');
        const cancelCustomBtn = document.getElementById('cancel-custom-btn');

        // Initialize game
        function initGame() {
            // Clear existing board
            boardElement.innerHTML = '';
            board = [];
            flagsCount = 0;
            revealedCount = 0;
            gameOver = false;
            firstClick = true;
            hintUsed = false;

            // Reset hint button
            hintBtn.disabled = false;
            hintBtn.style.opacity = '1';

            // Stop timer if running
            if (timerInterval) {
                clearInterval(timerInterval);
                timerInterval = null;
            }
            timer = 0;
            updateTimeDisplay();

            // Update mines count display
            minesCountElement.textContent = minesCount;
            flagsCountElement.textContent = flagsCount;

            // Set CSS variables for grid size
            boardElement.style.setProperty('--rows', rows);
            boardElement.style.setProperty('--cols', cols);

            // Create board
            for (let r = 0; r < rows; r++) {
                board[r] = [];
                for (let c = 0; c < cols; c++) {
                    board[r][c] = {
                        isMine: false,
                        isRevealed: false,
                        isFlagged: false,
                        adjacentMines: 0
                    };

                    const cell = document.createElement('div');
                    cell.className = 'cell';
                    cell.dataset.row = r;
                    cell.dataset.col = c;

                    // Event listeners
                    cell.addEventListener('click', () => handleLeftClick(r, c));
                    cell.addEventListener('contextmenu', (e) => {
                        e.preventDefault();
                        handleRightClick(r, c);
                    });

                    // Add touch support for mobile
                    cell.addEventListener('touchstart', (e) => {
                        e.preventDefault();
                        this.touchTimer = setTimeout(() => {
                            handleRightClick(r, c);
                        }, 500);
                    }, {passive: false});

                    cell.addEventListener('touchend', (e) => {
                        e.preventDefault();
                        clearTimeout(this.touchTimer);
                    }, {passive: false});

                    boardElement.appendChild(cell);
                }
            }
        }

        // Place mines after first click (to ensure first click is always safe)
        function placeMines(firstRow, firstCol) {
            let minesPlaced = 0;

            while (minesPlaced < minesCount) {
                const r = Math.floor(Math.random() * rows);
                const c = Math.floor(Math.random() * cols);

                // Don't place mine on first click or where a mine already exists
                if ((r !== firstRow || c !== firstCol) && !board[r][c].isMine) {
                    board[r][c].isMine = true;
                    minesPlaced++;
                }
            }

            // Calculate adjacent mines for each cell
            for (let r = 0; r < rows; r++) {
                for (let c = 0; c < cols; c++) {
                    if (!board[r][c].isMine) {
                        board[r][c].adjacentMines = countAdjacentMines(r, c);
                    }
                }
            }

            // Start timer after mines are placed
            startTimer();
        }

        // Count adjacent mines for a cell
        function countAdjacentMines(r, c) {
            let count = 0;

            // Check all 8 surrounding cells
            for (let dr = -1; dr <= 1; dr++) {
                for (let dc = -1; dc <= 1; dc++) {
                    if (dr === 0 && dc === 0) continue; // Skip current cell

                    const nr = r + dr;
                    const nc = c + dc;

                    // Check if neighbor is within bounds and is a mine
                    if (nr >= 0 && nr < rows && nc >= 0 && nc < cols && board[nr][nc].isMine) {
                        count++;
                    }
                }
            }

            return count;
        }

        // Handle left click
        function handleLeftClick(r, c) {
            if (gameOver || board[r][c].isFlagged) return;

            // On first click, place mines (avoiding this cell)
            if (firstClick) {
                placeMines(r, c);
                firstClick = false;
            }

            // If clicked on a mine
            if (board[r][c].isMine) {
                revealMines(r, c);
                gameOver = true;
                endGame(false);
                return;
            }

            // Reveal cell if not already revealed
            if (!board[r][c].isRevealed) {
                revealCell(r, c);

                // Check for win condition
                checkWin();
            } else {
                // If clicking on a revealed number, try chord action
                chordCells(r, c);
            }
        }

        // Handle right click (flag)
        function handleRightClick(r, c) {
            if (gameOver || board[r][c].isRevealed) return;

            const cell = getCellElement(r, c);

            if (!board[r][c].isFlagged) {
                board[r][c].isFlagged = true;
                cell.textContent = 'ðŸš©';
                flagsCount++;
                cell.classList.add('flagged');
            } else {
                board[r][c].isFlagged = false;
                cell.textContent = '';
                flagsCount--;
                cell.classList.remove('flagged');
            }

            flagsCountElement.textContent = flagsCount;
        }

        // Reveal a cell
        function revealCell(r, c) {
            if (board[r][c].isRevealed || board[r][c].isFlagged) return;

            const cell = getCellElement(r, c);
            board[r][c].isRevealed = true;
            cell.classList.add('revealed');
            revealedCount++;

            if (board[r][c].adjacentMines > 0) {
                cell.textContent = board[r][c].adjacentMines;
                cell.classList.add(`number-${board[r][c].adjacentMines}`);
            } else {
                // If no adjacent mines, reveal all adjacent cells recursively
                for (let dr = -1; dr <= 1; dr++) {
                    for (let dc = -1; dc <= 1; dc++) {
                        if (dr === 0 && dc === 0) continue; // Skip current cell

                        const nr = r + dr;
                        const nc = c + dc;

                        // Check if neighbor is within bounds
                        if (nr >= 0 && nr < rows && nc >= 0 && nc < cols) {
                            revealCell(nr, nc);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        // Chord action (when clicking on a revealed number)
        function chordCells(r, c) {
            const cell = board[r][c];
            if (!cell.isRevealed || cell.adjacentMines === 0) return;

            // Count adjacent flags
            let adjacentFlags = 0;
            for (let dr = -1; dr <= 1; dr++) {
                for (let dc = -1; dc <= 1; dc++) {
                    if (dr === 0 && dc === 0) continue;

                    const nr = r + dr;
                    const nc = c + dc;

                    if (nr >= 0 && nr < rows && nc >= 0 && nc < cols && board[nr][nc].isFlagged) {
                        adjacentFlags++;
                    }
                }
            }

            // If flags match adjacent mines, reveal all unflagged adjacent cells
            if (adjacentFlags === cell.adjacentMines) {
                for (let dr = -1; dr <= 1; dr++) {
                    for (let dc = -1; dc <= 1; dc++) {
                        if (dr === 0 && dc === 0) continue;

                        const nr = r + dr;
                        const nc = c + dc;

                        if (nr >= 0 && nr < rows && nc >= 0 && nc < cols && 
                            !board[nr][nc].isRevealed && !board[nr][nc].isFlagged) {

                            if (board[nr][nc].isMine) {
                                revealMines(nr, nc);
                                gameOver = true;
                                endGame(false);
                                return;
                            }

                            revealCell(nr, nc);
                        }
                    }
                }

                // Check for win condition after chording
                checkWin();
            }
        }

        // Reveal all mines (when game is lost)
        function revealMines(clickedR, clickedC) {
            for (let r = 0; r < rows; r++) {
                for (let c = 0; c < cols; c++) {
                    if (board[r][c].isMine) {
                        const cell = getCellElement(r, c);
                        cell.textContent = 'ðŸ’£';

                        if (r === clickedR && c === clickedC) {
                            cell.classList.add('mine-revealed');
                            setTimeout(() => {
                                cell.style.animation = 'explode 0.5s forwards';
                            }, 100);
                        } else {
                            cell.classList.add(board[r][c].isFlagged ? 'flagged' : 'mine-revealed');
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        // Check if player has won
        function checkWin() {
            if (revealedCount === (rows * cols - minesCount)) {
                gameOver = true;
                endGame(true);
                createConfetti();
            }
        }

        // End game (win or lose)
        function endGame(isWin) {
            // Stop timer
            if (timerInterval) {
                clearInterval(timerInterval);
                timerInterval = null;
            }

            if (isWin) {
                // Flag all mines if won
                for (let r = 0; r < rows; r++) {
                    for (let c = 0; c < cols; c++) {
                        if (board[r][c].isMine && !board[r][c].isFlagged) {
                            board[r][c].isFlagged = true;
                            const cell = getCellElement(r, c);
                            cell.textContent = 'ðŸš©';
                            cell.classList.add('flagged');
                        }
                    }
                }

                // Disable hint button completely
                hintBtn.disabled = true;
                hintBtn.style.opacity = '0.5';
            }

            // Show game over modal
            gameResultElement.textContent = isWin ? 'You Won! ðŸŽ‰' : 'Game Over! ðŸ’¥';
            gameStatsElement.textContent = `Time: ${timer} seconds | Mines: ${minesCount} | Size: ${rows}x${cols}`;
            gameOverModal.style.display = 'flex';
        }

        // Start timer
        function startTimer() {
            timer = 0;
            updateTimeDisplay();
            timerInterval = setInterval(() => {
                timer++;
                updateTimeDisplay();
            }, 1000);
        }

        // Update time display
        function updateTimeDisplay() {
            timeElement.textContent = timer;
        }

        // Get cell DOM element
        function getCellElement(r, c) {
            return document.querySelector(`.cell[data-row="${r}"][data-col="${c}"]`);
        }

        // Set difficulty
        function setDifficulty(difficulty) {
            switch (difficulty) {
                case 'easy':
                    rows = 10;
                    cols = 10;
                    minesCount = 10;
                    break;
                case 'medium':
                    rows = 16;
                    cols = 16;
                    minesCount = 40;
                    break;
                case 'hard':
                    rows = 16;
                    cols = 30;
                    minesCount = 99;
                    break;
                case 'custom':
                    // Custom settings handled separately
                    return;
            }

            // Update active button
            easyBtn.classList.remove('active');
            mediumBtn.classList.remove('active');
            hardBtn.classList.remove('active');
            customBtn.classList.remove('active');

            document.getElementById(`${difficulty}-btn`).classList.add('active');

            initGame();
        }

        // Show hint (reveal a safe cell)
        function showHint() {
            if (gameOver || firstClick || hintUsed) return;

            // Find all unrevealed, unflagged, non-mine cells
            const safeCells = [];
            for (let r = 0; r < rows; r++) {
                for (let c = 0; c < cols; c++) {
                    if (!board[r][c].isRevealed && !board[r][c].isFlagged && !board[r][c].isMine) {
                        safeCells.push({ r, c });
                    }
                }
            }

            if (safeCells.length > 0) {
                // Pick a random safe cell
                const { r, c } = safeCells[Math.floor(Math.random() * safeCells.length)];
                const cell = getCellElement(r, c);

                // Animation for hint
                cell.style.animation = 'highlight 1.5s ease-in-out';

                setTimeout(() => {
                    cell.style.animation = '';
                }, 1500);

                hintUsed = true;
                hintBtn.disabled = true;
                hintBtn.style.opacity = '0.5';
            }
        }

        // Create confetti effect for win
        function createConfetti() {
            const colors = ['#f00', '#0f0', '#00f', '#ff0', '#f0f', '#0ff'];
            const container = document.querySelector('.game-container');

            for (let i = 0; i < 100; i++) {
                const confetti = document.createElement('div');
                confetti.className = 'confetti';
                confetti.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
                confetti.style.backgroundColor = colors[Math.floor(Math.random() * colors.length)];
                confetti.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 2 + 's';
                container.appendChild(confetti);

                // Remove after animation
                setTimeout(() => {
                    confetti.remove();
                }, 3000);
            }
        }

        // Toggle theme
        function toggleTheme() {
            darkMode = !darkMode;

            if (darkMode) {
                document.body.classList.remove('light-mode');
                themeToggleBtn.textContent = 'ðŸŒ™ Dark Mode';
            } else {
                document.body.classList.add('light-mode');
                themeToggleBtn.textContent = 'â˜€ï¸ Light Mode';
            }
        }

        // Event listeners
        easyBtn.addEventListener('click', () => setDifficulty('easy'));
        mediumBtn.addEventListener('click', () => setDifficulty('medium'));
        hardBtn.addEventListener('click', () => setDifficulty('hard'));
        customBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            customModal.style.display = 'flex';
            document.getElementById('custom-rows').value = rows;
            document.getElementById('custom-cols').value = cols;
            document.getElementById('custom-mines').value = minesCount;
        });

        newGameBtn.addEventListener('click', initGame);
        playAgainBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            gameOverModal.style.display = 'none';
            initGame();
        });

        hintBtn.addEventListener('click', showHint);
        themeToggleBtn.addEventListener('click', toggleTheme);

        startCustomBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const customRows = parseInt(document.getElementById('custom-rows').value);
            const customCols = parseInt(document.getElementById('custom-cols').value);
            const customMines = parseInt(document.getElementById('custom-mines').value);

            // Validate inputs
            if (customRows < 5 || customRows > 30 || 
                customCols < 5 || customCols > 30 || 
                customMines < 3 || customMines > Math.floor(customRows * customCols * 0.5)) {
                alert('Invalid settings! Please check your inputs.');
                return;
            }

            rows = customRows;
            cols = customCols;
            minesCount = customMines;

            customModal.style.display = 'none';

            // Update active button
            easyBtn.classList.remove('active');
            mediumBtn.classList.remove('active');
            hardBtn.classList.remove('active');
            customBtn.classList.add('active');

            initGame();
        });

        cancelCustomBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            customModal.style.display = 'none';
        });

        // Initialize game on load
        initGame();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

This enhanced Minesweeper game now includes these animation improvements:

1. **Smooth Transitions**:
   - Smooth color transitions between light/dark modes
   - Animated button hovers with ripple effects
   - Fade-in animations for UI elements

2. **Cell Animations**:
   - Flip animation when revealing cells
   - Pulse effect when placing flags
   - Shake animation when hitting a mine
   - Explode animation for the mine you clicked

3. **Win/Lose Effects**:
   - Confetti particle effect when winning
   - Highlight animation for hint cells
   - Smooth modal appearances

4. **Enhanced Visual Feedback**:
   - Animated number reveals with 3D flip effect
   - Color-coded numbers with transitions
   - Dynamic shadow effects on hover

5. **Mobile Improvements**:
   - Touch support with long-press for flags
   - Responsive animations that work on all devices
   - Optimized performance for mobile

6. **UI Polish**:
   - Animated button click effects
   - Smooth transitions between game states
   - Enhanced visual hierarchy with animations

The game maintains all the original functionality while adding these visual enhancements to make gameplay more engaging and satisfying. The animations provide better feedback for player actions and make wins more exciting with the confetti celebration.

